{"tid":1234764,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[睇路]共產黨既五毛大軍已經殺入連登","createTime":"2019-06-17T03:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T04:16:12.000Z","uid":75735,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"390eadc1fdf8e0ab3c2c53e171efe4ecd020ab11","tid":1234764,"uid":75735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:52:18.000Z","msg":"大家小心唔好淨係上熱門版<br />\n成個熱門都係分化post 好得人驚<br />\n仲要咁撚多正評 <br />\n一定係有人帶緊風向 然後又有人中計<br />\n<br />\n大家有時間一定要睇一睇依篇轉載文<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1232173/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1232173/page/1</a><br />\n共產黨乜都廢 最勁就係玩分化戰<br />\n用網絡大軍改變風向 令你心灰 然後失去抗爭意識<br />\n千奇唔好中計<br />\n記住要用腦上連登<br />\n唔好見到多正皮就跟風<br />\n咁同廢老比長輩圖洗老冇分別<br />\n<br />\n有能力既話 唔好一味屌<br />\n見到人分化記得提醒兄弟們返轉頭<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登已經受到威脅<br />\n鍵盤戰士都要加油</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9a01c1ae6b439c114cf4f1e5e7d6cf5ece1e54d0","tid":1234764,"uid":74278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:52:59.000Z","msg":"千祈千祈唔好比人分化到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781e7e6eea92e1178ea9b6702c82b53a0b89d5b9","tid":1234764,"uid":24765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:53:27.000Z","msg":"冇錯 睇到好多負能量"},{"pid":"1a7958b46b0f20b854f9534a19d227ca58942350","tid":1234764,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ebe75604553eb308d82b44e0515a501720970c3","tid":1234764,"uid":75735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:54:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但唔好一味盲屌<br />\n只會令情況咁加惡劣<br />\n我地要<span style=\"color: green;\">提醒</span>比人唔小心帶走風向既兄弟<br />\n而家係非常時期<br />\n要團結一致<br />\n要保持我地士氣高漲</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7371b2037c041378a789137002018ad9e8f89432","tid":1234764,"uid":24765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:55:00.000Z","msg":"尤其是係深夜嘅時段𠴱陣<br />\n本身𠴱種大和解嘅氛圍變曬"},{"pid":"66223dfa1e183015236c0d7b85b768f1ea10d079","tid":1234764,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:59:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ba137313e0615e246ccca5698dd1ad912ceac4a","tid":1234764,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:01:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97dcdac93568a7ee258b6491f5ccbccea510bf43","tid":1234764,"uid":206344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:02:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3923ccf40ea3294b9bae345ad6399a2ad55ceea4","tid":1234764,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:03:12.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"d5a19d4b1d4b8608693986e42f66d1ee311e43ec","tid":1234764,"uid":56610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:06:18.000Z","msg":"大家睇路呀<br />\n唔好人話輸你就覺得輸<br />\n200萬人係歷史級別既數字<br />\n我地係完成緊一件歷史性既任務<br />\n啲人唔係先知<br />\n邊個會知下一秒發生咩事<br />\n啲人都係亂up鳩估<br />\n唔好信！<br />\n係二十一世紀<br />\n文字既殺傷力係超乎你想像！<br />\n保持理性同團結<br />\n記住林鄭點樣三番四次莫視香港人訴求<br />\n同佢果種不可一世既態度<br />\n<br />\n今次唔單止係為反送中而戰<br />\n反送中 救學生只係短期目標<br />\n今次我地要改變香港<br />\n踢走依個腐敗到極致既政府<br />\n實現真正既港人治港<br />\n<br />\n所以我地需要強大既意志力<br />\n香港人一條心！<br />\n咁多位兄弟加油！"},{"pid":"41b65367ae64f8db3c0904e0aaa44c370d84ca3d","tid":1234764,"uid":75735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:16:12.000Z","msg":"push"}]}